com.nokia.maps.kml

Interface Pair


  • public interface Pair
    This interface represents the <Pair> tag from KML specification. It defines a key/value pair that maps a mode (normal or highlight) to the predefined <styleUrl>

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static java.lang.String ELEMENT
      This constant defines <Pair> as an XML element.
      static java.lang.String KEY
      This constant defines an XML attribute defining the key of a pair.
      static java.lang.String STYLE_URL
      This constant defines an XML attribute defining the style url of a pair.

    • Method Summary
